  <entry>
    <title>git常见问题的解决办法</title>
    <url>/2022/07/18/git%E5%B8%B8%E8%A7%81%E9%97%AE%E9%A2%98%E7%9A%84%E8%A7%A3%E5%86%B3%E6%96%B9%E6%B3%95/</url>
    <content><![CDATA[<h1 id="Failed-to-connect-to-github-com-port-443-Timed-out"><a href="#Failed-to-connect-to-github-com-port-443-Timed-out" class="headerlink" title="Failed to connect to github.com port 443: Timed out"></a>Failed to connect to github.com port 443: Timed out</h1><p>先取消代理再设置代理</p>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global --unset http.proxy</span><br><span class="line">git config --global --unset https.proxy</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">git config --global https.proxy http://127.0.0.1:1080</span><br><span class="line">git config --global https.proxy https://127.0.0.1:1080</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure>
<h1 id="does-not-have-a-commit-checked-out"><a href="#does-not-have-a-commit-checked-out" class="headerlink" title="does not have a commit checked out"></a>does not have a commit checked out</h1><p>哪个文件夹报的错，删掉那个文件夹的.git</p>
<h1 id="fatal-unable-to-access-xxxxx-OpenSSL-SSL-read-Connection-was-reset-errno-10054"><a href="#fatal-unable-to-access-xxxxx-OpenSSL-SSL-read-Connection-was-reset-errno-10054" class="headerlink" title="fatal: unable to access xxxxx OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection was reset, errno 10054"></a>fatal: unable to access xxxxx OpenSSL SSL_read: Connection was reset, errno 10054</h1><p><code>git config --global http.sslVerify &quot;false&quot;</code></p>
]]></content>
  </entry>
